      <p>
        Mobile money services allow people to use their mobile phones as a 
        bank account. One can <m>{\color{blue} \text{deposit, withdraw or transfer}}</m> 
        money with their handsets. People can also <m>{\color{blue} \text{save}}</m> money and 
        <m>{\color{blue} \text{borrow}}</m> from mobile lenders. Mobile money transfer 
        is fast, easy and secure.
      </p>
